name: Warehouse (SoulSoph)
description:
Use the 1-9 keys to change the camera, use the q-e keys to look over to the door, use the a-d keys to lean into the vent.

ALL: Turn off the power to delay attacks

The day ends at 12:00 PM, not 6 AM, One hour takes 1 minute.

Please let me know if you encounter any bugs... I don't know how well ill be able to fix them (It's been over a year since I finished the game), but I will give it a shot.
